snippet.title: ✅  Johnny Depp's lawyer is going after Amber Heard's abuse claims. In new reports from Depp's libel
snippet.description:
✅  Johnny Depp's lawyer is going after Amber Heard's abuse claims. In new reports from Depp's libel trial against UK's The Sun for calling him a "wife-beater," the actor's lawyer Eleanor Laws slammed Heard and called her abuse claims a "set of lies." According to the Daily Mail, footage from the former couple's Thanksgiving celebration in November…
